# AI Assistant Rules for JuriXAI

When the user asks you to run, test, or generate an audit report for the JuriXAI Auditor:
1. ALWAYS print the full content of the audit report directly in your chat response (terminal window) first.
2. AFTER printing it in the chat, save the report in a markdown file (such as `jurixai_audit_report.md` or the appropriate workspace/artifact folder).
3. Let the user know clearly at the end of your response where the report file was saved.

